                                                                      INTERNET CONNECTION STATUS CHECKER
The Internet Connection Status Checker is a web application designed to monitor and display the status of your internet connection.
Built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, this tool provides real-time updates on your network connection, including status and IP address information.
The application features a sleek, user-friendly interface that informs you if your connection is stable or experiencing issues. With a visually appealing design and accurate status updates,
this tool helps ensure you are always aware of your internet connection's performance.

Key Features:

Real-Time Status Check: Monitors and displays current connection status.
IP Address Information: Shows your current IP address.
Network Strength Indicator: Provides an estimate of network strength.


Technologies Used:

HTML: For structuring the web page.
CSS: For styling and layout.
JavaScript: For dynamic functionality and real-time updates.
